{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>到 joomla1.7 安装目录找到 <code>configuration.php</code> 文件记事本打开将</p>\n<pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"text html php\"><span>...</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"text html php\"><span>public&nbsp;$force_ssl&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;2&#39;;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"text html php\"><span>...</span></span></div></pre>\n<p>修改成</p>\n<pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"text html php\"><span>...</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"text html php\"><span>public&nbsp;$force_ssl&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;0&#39;;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"text html php\"><span>...</span></span></div></pre>\n<p>访问后台，重新设置，就跟什么都没发生一样。</p>\n<hr>","frontmatter":{"path":"/88FxdZhGGnRgwuWPCVPels8l","title":"joomla1.7 开启SSL无法访问问题","date":"2012-02-15 10:29:56 +0800","comments":true,"categories":"programming","author":"Sir0xb","tags":["joomla"]}}},"pageContext":{}}